Package org.example.model.playarea

Class Node

java.lang.Object
org.example.model.playarea.PlaceHolder
org.example.model.playarea.Node
public class Node extends PlaceHolder
Class for the placement of cards. The node is an Object with 4 connections to other nodes. You can go to every node only from the beginner. This class uses iterators to avoid ConcurrentModificationException when modifying lists during iteration.
